Second Leg
[Apr 17]
Vitória         0-0  Bahia

Vitória is the 2005 Bahia State champions!

Relegation Playoff
First Leg
[Jun 4]
Palmeiras       1-1  Camaçariense

Second Leg
[Jun 11]
Camaçariense    0-0  Palmeiras

Palmeiras relegatet to Second Division 2006.


